Heat oven to 375 degrees F. Beat butter, sugars, dry pudding mix and vanilla in large bowl with mixer until blended. Add eggs and baking soda; mix well. Gradually beat in flour. Stir in remaining ingredients. Drop tablespoons of dough, 2 inches apart, onto baking sheets. Bake 8 to 10 min. or until golden brown. Cool on baking sheets 1 min. Remove to wire racks; cool completely.